{"tid":2395804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"GME, 返送中, 魚蛋革命 告誡我們. 人是為強權服務, 民主只是口號.","createTime":"2021-02-05T06:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T06:42:33.000Z","uid":311611,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"34eb5bc3ec08af5234c8072199dc47a534a78e12","tid":2395804,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:27:46.000Z","msg":"天地不仁, 以萬物為芻狗<br />\n美國不仁,  以散戶為芻狗<br />\n香港不仁,  以黑衫為芻狗<br />\n中國不仁,  以低端人口, 異己為芻狗<br />\n<br />\n你以為Gphone 上到做特首就會好? 你錯了, 咪又係打壓異己. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但似你要記住, 天地, 中國, 美國, 香港 佢地養活左唔少人. <br />\n<br />\n民主只係口號, 實在一無是處. 追求民主既人, 只會整親自己.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d595414964770ab359de35971cbdb1652ad4711f","tid":2395804,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e82e423230f7c01fbb04c9d598ee314c25a46e","tid":2395804,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"91925982215bd855cbc5a304dfc06aa555ee0440","tid":2395804,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599f8a4e3526e16258d322ab9d12b1f4096dec06","tid":2395804,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94fddccbd5286b18b99227fbc3eee33755fba43","tid":2395804,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"無人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}